title: "Kate Kafe" Coffee Shop Font
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131106102101im_/http:/typophile.com/files/j0ph_4026.png)

Found this on a local coffee shop's website. Could not find any other uses throughout the website. Any information would be greatly appreciated!
author: LordZero2

comments.content:
It must be **[Katy Berry](http://web.archive.org/web/20131106102101/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-1&ffam=Katy%20Berry%20-%20Regular&fid=0aa9e03a25fba77e11c791dd8e8e1cb2&fsize=60&text=Kate%20Kafe&fit=1)** by Andrew Hart (Dirt2.com, 2009, Free for personal use)
